# pfse_starterkit
A Python package that installs all required packages for Structural Python core training for Python version >= 3.13.

This installs the following packages:

* numpy
* pandas
* openpyxl
* lxml
* shapely
* matplotlib
* plotly
* sectionproperties
* concreteproperties
* pycba
* PyNiteFEA
* scipy
* handcalcs
* more-itertools
* pynite_plotly
* forallpeople
* pytest
* rich
* tqdm
* papermodels
* xlwings
* IPython
* ipywidgets
* ipykernel
* jupyterlab
* jupyterlab-mathjax3
* nbconvert
* python-docx
* pynite-tools
* sectionproperties-tools
* papermill
* great-tables
